  "Description": {
    "English": "Aligns the ship's electromagnetic emissions with <span class=\"name name-fuel\">A T L A S</span> waves, providing basic propulsion and Pulse Jump capability.<br> <br>The sub-light drive hungers for <span class=\"name name-exotic\">tritium</span> or <span class=\"name name-special\">radiant shards</span>.<br><br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span> to engage Pulse Jump.<br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> to initiate in-flight speed boost.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使飞船的电磁辐射与<span class=\"name name-fuel\">阿特拉斯</span>波调谐，并借此提供基础的推进与脉冲跃迁能力。<br><br>亚光速驱动器需要<span class=\"name name-exotic\">氚</span>或者<span class=\"name name-special\">光耀碎片</span>。<br><br>长按<span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span>启动脉冲跃迁。<br>长按<span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>在飞行中进行速度提升。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "校準太空船電磁輻射的頻率，與<span class=\"name name-fuel\">寰 宇</span>電磁波同步，提供基本推進與脈衝跳躍能力。<br><br>次光速驅動器渴望著<span class=\"name name-exotic\">氚</span>或<span class=\"name name-special\">發光裂片</span>的能量。<br><br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span> 發動脈衝跳躍。<br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> 啟動飛行加速功能。"
  },
